907
01:26:38,566 --> 01:26:40,978
Vamos disparar, Cpt. Nagata!

908
01:26:50,745 --> 01:26:52,748
Capitão Nagata!

909
01:26:56,219 --> 01:26:57,787
Fogo!

910
